<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>跳过数据，限制查询数量   （网站分页）</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="shiki one-dark-pro" style="background-color: #282c34" tabindex="0"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #E5C07B">User</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">.</span><span style="color: #61AFEF">find</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">().</span><span style="color: #61AFEF">skip</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">(</span><span style="color: #D19A66">2</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">).</span><span style="color: #61AFEF">limit</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">(</span><span style="color: #D19A66">3</span><span style="color: #ABB2BF">)</span></span>
