<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="shiki one-dark-pro" style="background-color: #282c34" tabindex="0"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">// User.updateOne({查询条件},{要更改的值}).then(result=&gt;{console.log(result);})</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #7F848E; font-style: italic">// 返回值 { n: 1, nModified: 1, ok: 1 } n：代表更新几条数据 ok：代表更新成功</span></span>
