<li>
<div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-ext="text"><pre v-pre class="shiki one-dark-pro" style="background-color: #282c34" tabindex="0"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #abb2bf">启用静态资源服务功能</span></span>
